title: The Strongest God of War in the City
description: Ning Bei suffered a family rebellion when he was young, and fled to the northern border alone. For thirteen years, he honed himself as the invincible god of war in the northern border, and protected his home country with a northern king sword. One day, Ning Bei returned to dragon city and faced the battle again. Once love and hatred, his road to revenge began. The Strongest God of War in the City Dushi Zui Qiang Zhanshen The City’s Strongest God of War 都市最强战神
